Class IASValueBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eso.ias.prototype.input.java.IASValueBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IASValue

    public abstract class IASValueBase
extends java.lang.Object
    The view of the untyped heterogeneous inputs in the java code. Objects of this class are immutable i.e. updating returns a new immutable object
